        <mxCell id="intent-fields" value="• id, created_at&#xa;• question : str (natural language)&#xa;• grounding : EntityRef[]  (must cite L2)&#xa;• reasoning_trace : L4 output&#xa;• proposed_action : ActionProposal?&#xa;• salience : 0.0 – 1.0&#xa;• confidence : 0.0 – 1.0&#xa;• status : pending | executing | done&#xa;           | dismissed | failed" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;spacingLeft=10" vertex="1" parent="1">
