        <mxCell id="action-fields" value="• id, intent_id, timestamp&#xa;• category : safe | suggest | ask&#xa;• operation : plugin-qualified&#xa;     e.g. homeassistant.turn_on&#xa;• parameters : object&#xa;• result : object?&#xa;• signature : ed25519&#xa;• reversible_by : action-id | manual steps&#xa;&#xa;Forced-approval classes:&#xa;  finance · messaging · locks · security" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;spacingLeft=10" vertex="1" parent="1">
