        <mxCell id="autonomy-fields" value="• default_slider : float (0.4)&#xa;• domains : Map&lt;str, DomainConfig&gt;&#xa;  – slider : float (0.0–1.0)&#xa;  – action_classes : list[str]&#xa;• hard_ask : list[HardAskRule]&#xa;  – action_class, reason&#xa;• graduation : GraduationConfig&#xa;  – enabled, min_approvals (10)&#xa;  – min_approval_rate (0.8)&#xa;  – max_promotion (0.1)&#xa;  – promotion_cooldown_days (7)" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=10;spacingLeft=10" vertex="1" parent="1">
